title: Planetary Physics.Astronomy - 4 Books (gnv64)
description:
Here is a collection of 4 PDFs on planetary physics/astronomy.
DO NOT USE Adobe reader which may give problems.
Instead, use Foxit, Sumatra or Calibre.

1. An Introduction to Planetary Atmospheres by by Agustin Sanchez-Lavega
   https://www.amazoncom/Introduction-Planetary-Atmospheres-Agustin-Sanchez-Lavega/dp/142006732X
2. Planetary Science - The Science of Planets around Stars (2nd Ed) by by George H. A. Cole and Michael M. 

Woolfson
   http://www.amazoncom/Planetary-Science-Planets-around-Second/dp/146656315X
3. Quest for the Origin of Particles and the Universe by by Yasumichi Aoki and Kiyoshi Hayasaka
   http://www.amazoncom/Quest-Origin-Particles-Universe-Yasumichi-ebook/dp/B00DBLZGKO
4. The Physics of Reality - Space, Time, Matter, Cosmos by by Richard L Amoroso and Louis H Kauffman
   http://www.amazoncom/Physics-Reality-Proceedings-Mathematical-Jean-Pierre/dp/B00P6JLL8U
